text:
(Tenka... Is she getting help from
Amana with her assignment?)

Tenka-chan,
I finished the English assignment for you~!

(...No,
This is more than just helping...)

You shouldn't let
Amana do it all.

I think assignments should be done
by oneself to have meaning.

Ugh... but...
Tenka alone... doesn't have enough time...!

Tenka has been busy lately...
If there's something I can do...

Eh...!! Then...
The math one... please...!

So... Producer-san will...
solve it for me...?
